snippet.title: SnowRunner Jeep Dual Pack - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Saber Interactive and Focus Entertainment have partnered with Jeep to bring two iconic Jeep trucks to the SnowRunner garage in the Jeep Dual Pack. The new pack is available to buy now on PC, PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and Nintendo Switch as standalone SnowRunner DLC. Check out the Wrangler-Rubicon and the CJ-7 "Renegade" Jeep SnowRunner vehicles in motion in this trailer.

#GameTrailers #Gaming #SnowRunner
